# Local environment overrides — secrets (LOCAL_JWT_SECRET, bootstrap admin
# password, SSO client id, etc.) MUST NOT be committed. Templates
# (.env.example) and branch-specific build-time configs (.env.production,
# .env.e2e) are intentionally tracked and whitelisted below.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.production
!.env.e2e
!.env.sandbox
